Title: Leap of Faith
Plot: The NCIS team is called in to stop a naval officer from committing suicide by jumping off a rooftop, but when the suicide attempt turns into a murder, the NCIS team will have to find out who did it.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Titus Welliver, Robin Thomas, Brian Dietzen, Susan Kelechi Watson, Alaina Huffman, Adam Huss, John Vickery, Mark Matkevich, Deanna Russo
